## Pushing
{% block git_push_instructions -%}
- Never force push. Always use regular commits and `git push`.
- **Exception — rebase to resolve conflicts:**
  1. Create and push a backup branch: `duo-developer-backup/<branch>`
  2. Rebase, then push with `git push --force-with-lease`
  3. Post a comment on the MR explaining what was done
- Never rewrite history (squash, amend) without explicit user instruction.
